            <title>OPPO 預告衞星通訊機能，將於下代 Find X 旗艦機提供</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/13/oppo-find-x7-satellite-communication-support/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=oppo-find-x7-satellite-communication-support</link>
